listitem.para:
This option will add custom options to the main menu. It is an array of arrays listing the caption, access level required, and the link to be executed. For example:
$g_main_menu_custom_options = array( array( 'My Link', MANAGER, 'my_link.php' ), array( 'My Link2', ADMINISTRATOR, 'my_link2.php' ), );
Note that if the caption is found in the Custom Strings File (see ) it will be replaced by the corresponding translated string. Options will only be added to the menu if the current logged in user has the appropriate access level.
